        "TextSection": {
            "TextSectionType": "Definition",
            "Contents": "A rare epidermolysis bullosa simplex characterized by the association of the typical trauma-induced blisters with additional features including hearing impairment alopecia hypo- or anodontia and nail dystrophy. Occurrence of vitiliginous skin areas unrelated to the sites of the blisters has also been described."
        },
